{"type": "article", "id": 2200, "title": "Vitra 经典墙面收纳", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:09:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222252QIYA57CmBGyOhlLd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t2.Uten.Silo by Dorothee Becker\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t所谓经典大抵就是长久不衰地流行。德国女设计师 Dorothee Becker 1969 年为 Vitra 设计的这款墙面收纳装置 Uten.Silo 至今仍是 Vitra 产品中的热销款，透出浓浓的复古风情。Uten.Silo 面世后广受好评，此后还推出了尺寸较小的版本。Uten.Silo 拥有各种大小及形状的收纳盒以及挂钩，能够保证许多日常用品被收纳其中，且很容易被找到。售价 395 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.vitra.com/en-us/product/utensilo#\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134901j9e5JhroTYugZqSH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134901CUFe8k7xJ6NyhM9j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.284375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134902PVeoMGp7wWItCsgJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}